title: Dione Santos
text:
Dione Francisco dos Santos (born 25 July 1979) is a former <a href="Brazil">Brazil</a>ian <a href="association%20football">football</a> player.
Club career.
He made his <a href="Primeira%20Liga">Primeira Liga</a> debut for <a href="Vit%C3%B3ria%20F.C.">Vitória Setúbal</a> on 13 March 2005 in a game against <a href="Vit%C3%B3ria%20S.C.">Vitória Guimarães</a>.
